<article><a href="http://hhsw.de/sites/proto/boo/" class="ScreenshotLink"><img src="screenshots/boo.jpg" alt="Boo Screenshot"/></a>

<a name="boo"><h2>Boo</h2></a>
<p class="Stats"><time datetime="2014-10">October 2014</time> • $(loc ../Boo htdocs) • JavaScript • Unlicense</p>
<p>You're a ghost trying to hide from the priests that want to free your soul.</p>
<p>Don't let them touch you! Click on a free spot to survive as long as you can.</p>
<p>This is kind of a follow up of a <a href="games-0h-game-jam.html#huh">game</a> I made for <a href="http://0hgame.eu/">0h Game Jam</a>.</p>
<ul class="ProjectLinks Separator">
<li><a href="http://hhsw.de/sites/proto/boo/" class="Primary">Play</a></li>
